1.name: DragonAska
1.desc: The legendary dragon is one of the symbols of fire-type Elemons. Their power comes from the ability to manipulate lava magma and rocks.

2.name: PrimeDragonAska
2.desc: Regarded as one of the most powerful evolved Elemons in Elematris, he alone can battle Corruptor's army of over 3000 monsters.

3.name: RaxMirade
3.desc: Dominating the sky, flying at lightning speed, their true form is hardly seen. During the war against Corruptor's minions, RaxMirade plays an important role in moving the other Elemons to the rallying location.

4.name: Neikoo
4.desc: One of the rare Elemons with a cute appearance, but has a source of fearsome power inside. Neikoo has the ability to absorb light waves around and from there generate energy for himself.

5.name: Raimaster
5.desc: A descendant of the Raizer, possessing superior overall physicality, strength as well as a versatile skill set. The result of research into Elemon evolution by the top professors in Elematris.

6.name: Raizer
6.desc: Elematris' assassin, without eyes but still able to move very flexibly, all directions are sensed by his extremely sensitive sense of smell. The weapons attached to his arms as part of his body help him to achieve superior level and skill.

7.name: Earkoo
7.desc: Fat and cute, his hobby is sleeping. In the war against the minions of Corruptor, it is Earkoo who uses his bulky body to block the powerful laser beams from evil modern machines.

8.name: Skurumi
8.desc: Though a herbivore, the Skurumi is not gentle. Their power is always formidable whether in the middle of the ocean or on the continents. Dubbed the sea monster of Elematris, he terrifies anyone who hears this name.

9.name: RusMoonch
9.desc: One of the gentlest and cutest Elemons in the land of Elematris. In the battle against the minions of Corruptor, Rus Moonch always shows courage, steadfastness far beyond his lovely appearance.

10.name: PoxArchies
10.desc: Small and agile, extremely flexible in using his skills. Nicknamed Flying Squirrel.

11.name: Legolas
11.desc: Fierce and scary as it looks. With the ability to manipulate water, Legolas can create tsunamis with great destructive power.

12.name: Mykasa
12.desc: Small and lovely, Mykasa always brings laughters to those around her. However, don't anger Mykasa, her screams can cause severe damage.

13.name: Cokoner
13.desc: As the mascot of one of Elematris lands, always fond of angering Legolas, Cokoner's prowess has been demonstrated in two battles with Corruptor's minions.

15.name: Hyugar
15.desc: Mascot of Mangetor, one of the leaders of Elematris. With skills that deal massive damage, Hyugar is always the first choice in every battle.

16.name: Inori
16.desc: Coming from the sea of Ran Axter with Legolas, both have the ability to control water to create tsunamis, but the two are far different in appearance.

17.name: Elight
17.desc: Jump jump jump jump!!!Jump jump jump jump!!! Likes lollipops and music. Elight can use his musical waves to deal damage to enemies.

18.name: SkyGaden
18.desc: Electric-type summon beast with the ability to emit electric shock waves up to 5000 volts, but to perform this skill requires a lot of time, this is also SkyGaden biggest weakness.

19.name: Scary
19.desc: A stone without a soul, very obedient. Scary has the ability to emit large electrically charged waves that can cause long-term paralysis.

20.name: Finter
20.desc: One of the Elemons who returned to the mysterious land filled with toxic smoke and electric clouds called Vondertera. Contrary to his cute appearance, Finter possesses dark sides with extremely petrifying powers.

21.name: Ties
21.desc: Scary ghosts, they can face the sunlight without leaving a shadow under their feet. Their eyes are filled with magic that petrifies any enemy with one glance.

22.name: Kuroo
22.desc: The creator of a powerful potion that weakens and reduces healing. Kuroo can formulate poisons with no antidote that scare away any enemy.

26.name: Hoorus
26.desc: Kind and lovely, can support healing very well, indispensable in every squad.

27.name: CorsairMastic
27.desc: One of Corsair's five Elemons was sent to Elematris to help fight the Corruptor.
